reviewText: I was expecting more to this video than what I got. I read about it before I got it but it didn't live up to it's billing.

This stunning Playgirl presentation of the 1997 Mr Nude Universe pageant is a superb exhibition of succulent male flesh.

 A dozen of the sexiest male strippers, exotic dancers and musclemen take it all off in a bid to win the coveted Mr Nude title. They strut, dance and strip their way through this competition for the pleasure of their female audience, these hot men love to entertain, and have no problems with exposing thier huge assets in full-frontal. Each of these hunks have bodies so perfectly sexy in thier muscular tone, so beautiful and well endowed that picking a winner or choosing a favourite is next to impossible.

A great DVD for a girls night in, and a must have for a girls erotica collection.

Now, take it all off boys!!! Shake it!!!!!!
